1. *Nagradu* je dobio tata. (He was awarded the prize.)
2. Ona je dobila nagradu za najbolju knjigu. (She was awarded a prize for the best book.)
3. Onima koji su se takmičili nagrade su dodeljene na ceremoniji. (The prizes were awarded to those who competed at the ceremony.)
4. On je često nagrađivan za svoj rad. (He was often rewarded for his work.)
5. Naši studenti su nagrađeni za svoje uspehe. (Our students were rewarded for their accomplishments.)